  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This belt holds four miniaturized bottles intended for healing potions. Each bottle holds half of a healing potion.</p>\n<p>As a bonus action, a creature can drink the content of one of the bottles and regain hit points equal to half the maximum of the potion used.</p>\n<p>For example, a @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-items.ZSzeMxEcEFiaxbdx]{Potion of Healing} heals up to <strong>10 hit points</strong>, so drinking this miniature bottle heals <strong>5 hit points</strong>.</p>",
